README

This Project contains all used code in the creation of the Paper: "Long-term measurements of Ice-Nucleating Particles in the Southern Ocean Region" by Schmitt et al. (in preparation)

The code is spit up in two Folders. Figure contains all code used in the creation of the figures. Analysis contains all code related to the Analysis.

